Class WCNForecastWeatherQueryFn

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--WCNForecastWeatherQueryFn
public class WCNForecastWeatherQueryFn
extends java.lang.Object
implements EDU.cmu.softagents.infoagents.ExternalQueryFn.ExternalQueryInterface

An external query function capable of extracting weather forecast information from Weather Channel Web site weather pages. Note that this is heavily adapted from example InfoAgent external query functions supplied by the CMU RETSINA support organization.
